A man was shot dead while another was critically wounded in a shootout at the Makhetha Shopping Centre in Soweto on Friday morning.Police spokesperson Kay Makhubela said an unidentified number of people in a white sedan shot at a parked minibus taxi outside the shopping complex and drove off.The survivor is said to be in critical condition. Makhubela said a case of murder and attempted murder has been opened.Arrests are yet to be made.Source: News24